n. 显性（性状），显性基因

sentences.en: Economically, the centre of Spain has lost its dominant role.
sentences.cn: 西班牙中部在经济上已失去了其主导地位。

sentences.en: The image or the image patterns can certainly be recognized as the dominant device.
sentences.cn: 图像或图像模式当然可以被识别为主导设备。

sentences.en: The dominant theoretical model of leadership at the moment is, apparently, the "transformational leadership pattern".
sentences.cn: 显然，目前领导者的主导理论模型是“变革型领导模式”。
